# SETU Website — Engineering Context

## Stack

- **React 19 + Vite 8** — `setu_website/`
- **Tailwind CSS 4** — design tokens (`setu-*`, `#1C39BB` brand blue)
- **Express** mini API — `server/index.js` (contact form); most data via proxied backend services
- **Parity target:** `setuReactNative` screens and API clients

## Architecture

- **Marketing:** `/` — public landing
- **Auth:** `/login`, `/register/*` — OTP user, VLE ID+password, district coordinator
- **App shell:** `/app/*` — logged-in user (AppLayout)
- **VLE portal:** `/vle/*` — VLELayout (dashboard, register user, wallet, leaderboard)
- **API proxy:** Vite dev proxy + `public/api/staging-proxy.php` — prefixes `/auth`, `/jobs`, etc.

## Auth

- Session in `AuthContext` + `localStorage` (`setu_auth_session`)
- SETU-AUTH refresh via `/auth/refreshToken` only
- VLE tokens: separate JWT + refresh in `src/api/roleAuth.js`
- Never hardcode staging/production API hosts in pages — use `src/config/api.js`

## Key Paths

| Area | Path |
|------|------|
| Routes | `src/App.jsx` |
| API clients | `src/api/*.js` |
| VLE pages | `src/pages/vle/` |
| Layouts | `src/layouts/` |
| Proxy config | `vite.config.js`, `.env` (`VITE_PROXY_*`) |

## Local Dev

- Website: `npm run dev` → `:5173`
- SETU-AUTH local: `VITE_PROXY_AUTH_HOST=http://localhost:7005` in `.env`
- Gateway path: `/auth/api/vle/...` → SETU-AUTH `/api/vle/...`

## Team Standards

- Implement only what was asked; match RN behaviour before inventing UX
- Run `npm run build` before claiming UI work is done
- Conventional Commits enforced by Husky — see `CONTRIBUTING.md`
